"""
Little Bighorn — Last Stand  (25 June 1876)
Engine: Panda3D      pip install panda3d

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  DROP MODELS HERE:   models/
    trooper.glb       Union cavalry soldier
    horse.glb         War pony
    warrior.glb       Lakota/Cheyenne rider
    dead.glb          Fallen figure (optional)

  Where to get free models:
    • Sketchfab.com  — filter: free + downloadable
      search "US cavalry", "Native American warrior", "horse"
    • Mixamo.com     — free rigged humans (needs Blender export)
    • poly.pizza     — free low-poly models

  If a model file is missing the game falls back to the
  procedural box-mesh version automatically.

  Per-pixel lighting (render.setShaderAuto) is enabled
  automatically when any .glb model is loaded.
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Controls:
  W/S        — Move forward / backward
  A/D        — Strafe left / right
  Mouse      — Look (captured)
  Left click — Fire
  R          — Reload
  Tab        — Switch weapon  (Carbine ↔ Colt)
  ESC        — Quit
"""

